h, monastery’. Places in Buckinghamshire, Cambridgeshire, Lincolnshire, Northamptonshire, and Staffordshire having this origin use the spelling <i>Stowe</i>, but the spelling difference cannot be relied on as an indication of locality of origin. The final <i>-e</i> in part represents a trace of the Old English dative inflection.","Americanized form of various like-sounding Jewish surnames.","Chinese: variant Romanization of the surname 司徒, see   Situ  ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Randulphus Stoke married Randulphus Stoke before 1092, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1038–1127":"1038–1127","1092–1180":"1092–1180","–Female":"Surnud","1127":"1127","1038":"1038","before 1092":"enne 1092","1092":"1092","1180":"1180","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1038–1127":"1038–1127","1092–1180":"1092–1180","–Female":"Kuollut","1127":"1127","1038":"1038","before 1092":"ennen vuotta 1092","1092":"1092","1180":"1180","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1038–1127":"1038–1127","1092–1180":"1092–1180","–Female":"Décédée","1127":"1127","1038":"1038","before 1092":"avant 1092","1092":"1092","1180":"1180","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mrs Randulphus Stoke a épousé Randulphus Stoke avant 1092, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1038–1127":"1038–1127","1092–1180":"1092–1180","–Female":"Verstorben","1127":"1127","1038":"1038","before 1092":"vor 1092","1092":"1092","1180":"1180","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England","England":"England","lifeSummary":"Mrs Randulphus Stoke hat vor 1092 in England Randulphus Stoke geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1038–1127":"1038–1127","1092–1180":"1092–1180","–Female":"Desede","1127":"1127","1038":"1038","before 1092":"before 1092","1092":"1092","1180":"1180","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England","England":"England